		<title>04TOM ARMSTRONG (POTTER)</title>
		<content>           Tom Armstrong (Potter)      
                                       
    During our visit to Kilroot Park we
 had a brief visit to Tom Armstrong the
 potter.                               
    He makes mostly{domestic hardware  
 but makes some{decorative things}as   
 well.                                 
    He exports{25% of his products to  
{America}and the rest just goes to     
 local shops for them to sell.         
    His material for making the pottery
 comes from{Stoke on Trent.}He started 
 18 months ago and only employs        
 himself.                              
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       </content>
